|---|---|---|

caption: Table 1: Number of attempts and success rate for each request type
description: This table presents the results of experiments conducted to evaluate the performance of the proposed robotic system on three types of user requests: simple, moderately complex, and complex.  For each request type, it indicates the number of attempts made and the corresponding success rate, showcasing the system's effectiveness across different levels of task complexity.  The results highlight the varying success rates for different task complexities.
